  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca 931\u0d9a \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The fuel license of 931 fuel stations is valid",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Minister of Electricity and Energy Kanchana Wijesekera said that the National Fuel License was implemented in 931 fuel stations today. He also mentions that 4.6 million vehicles have been registered in the system so far.",
        "He said that 140,605 transactions were done using the National Fuel License and the amount of fuel used was 1,086,282 liters."
      ],
